{"tid":1672334,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［舊文重推］加泰集會 去既唔該醒水 大家自行執生","createTime":"2019-10-24T04:56:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T11:32:45.000Z","uid":103618,"like":50,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"bd1a085e9819f9874fbe58948fb98a7f945b4c95","tid":1672334,"uid":103618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T04:56:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">唔想俾左膠外媒扭曲個集會<br />\n當場執生好過齋食事後丸<br />\n</span></span><br />\n在場人士唔該帶齊工具<br />\n- 各種警暴文宣標語（香港/加泰/各國）<br />\n- 各國國旗<br />\n- (Optional) 11月2日集會文宣<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">Do：</span></span><br />\n(1) 記得<ins>將注意力擺落警暴/人權問題 </ins><br />\n例如：標語唔好模糊用字齋寫「撐加泰」，要詳細講明撐咩（例如 #Police Brutality #Don'tLearnFromCCP ）<br />\n<br />\n(2) 如果有手足做左/講左啲咩好有詮釋空間既嘢，唔該幫手兜番<br />\n例如：舉加獨旗，唔該幫手舉埋各國國旗（人權係普世價值啊）<br />\n<br />\n(3) 如有搗亂份子，大家識執生<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Don't:</span></span><br />\n(1) 舉港獨旗<br />\n(2) 講加泰政治<br />\n<br />\n詳細Post見：<br />\n[加泰集會] [集思廣益] 不分化不割席補救Post [中/Eng]<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1671845\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1671845</a><br />\n<br />\n其實大家都係醒目仔女，一定有唔少方法令今次集會唔好錯Focus，歡迎討論，一齊Be Water<br />\n<br />\n小弟言盡於此，同意請推<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"5d19a71960b254419b3c79b79c0bb5c4f93543fb","tid":1672334,"uid":103618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T04:57:14.000Z","msg":"自推1/10"},{"pid":"1925bee8da8bc94182613a4480ef26378156baa1","tid":1672334,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T04:57:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>SUCK 1026長龍爆買日<br />\n18區爆買日目標黃店（一）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PiTw4ry.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPiTw4ry.png&h=6278c244&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3r8AMEZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thum