-24T05:16:03.000Z","msg":"16/20<br />\n如果要去既<br />\n焦點在<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">警暴</span></span><br />\n唔好再討論任何立場，呢個唔係立場Post係補救Post<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e944b655783f277c5fabd8181b5f12f51fa668b","tid":1672334,"uid":103618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0370cdee21e39670ff8942d0dab05b9fc6bfa730","tid":1672334,"uid":103618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T05:07:09.000Z","msg":"13/20<br />\n呢個係「預防」post，歡迎大家拋建議點樣令媒體唔好亂炒<br />\n如果最後多手足去就要幫手正視聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果無咩手足去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T05:19:22.000Z","msg":"17/20<br />\n我在重申，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">呢度唔係討論應唔應該去</span></span>，呢啲野大家自行判斷 除非集會取消左不然都實有人去<br />\n呢度講<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"> 如果手足去做，可以點做</span></span><br />\n最重要係<br />\n（1）多手足去，大家點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（2）無咩手足去，甘唔洗煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地直接宣傳11月2日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0173cf4c1f49f8a48f933516e7cc74d07ac26d8","tid":1672334,"uid":112878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T05:19:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ac069986a6a3d89d5028ee423ac7055a44ea4a0f","tid":1672334,"uid":103618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4fcc6230f51ab2fda980f296805a223009cf67e","tid":1672334,"uid":290176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd1a085e9819f9874fbe58948fb98a7f945b4c95","tid":1672334,"uid":103618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T04:56:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">唔想俾左膠外媒扭曲個集會<br />\n當場執生好過齋食事後丸<br />\n</span></span><br />\n在場人士唔該帶齊工具<br />\n- 各種警暴文宣標語（香港/加泰/