9-10-24T05:27:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">一、誠意推薦：</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><em>香港大專學界國際事務代表團眾籌計劃</em></strong><br />\nHong Kong IAD Crowdfunding Plan<br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fhkiad-crowdfunding%2F&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUoTMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=d2bc755d\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><em>香港眾志國際眾籌計劃 Demosisto International Campaign Crowdfunding Project</em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%259C%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E7%259C%25BE%25E7%25B1%258C%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project%2F%3Fshow_desktop%3D1&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUoTMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=46548925\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">二、什麼是遊說集團？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n遊說集團的工作，<strong><ins>是嘗試影響立法者</ins></strong>或其他持份者決定或行為，在政治角力中為服務對象<strong><ins>爭取利益</ins></strong>。遊說集團的服務對象，可以是國家、企業、社會團體、個人。在美國，政治遊說是極為普遍及重要的一環；幾乎所有政治操作都有遊說集團的參與。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">三、為什麼香港需要遊說隊伍？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n任何國家的政治，背後都擁有複雜的政治脈絡；包括國家政策、政治形勢、民意、錯綜複雜的利益網絡、乃至個別官員或議員的性情喜好。要在國際社會維護和爭取香港的利益，<strong><ins>香港需要一支能具經驗和技巧，能夠有效收風、熟識政治形勢</ins></strong>、具備遊說策略的隊伍。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">四、遊說集團？對家一早做緊啊！</span></span></strong><br />\n【華為被禁】華為遊說費飆60倍！原來聘用特朗普籌款人 欲說服白宮<br />\n<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2479940?r=cpsdlc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2479940%3Fr%3Dcpsdlc&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUoTMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=7759a62c\" target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2479940?r=cpsdlc</a><br />\n<br />\n董建華基金會 擲2,240萬左右美政策<br />\n大搞政治游說 否認中共代理人<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171130/20230175\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171130%2F20230175&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUoTMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=1d47c54a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171130%2F20230175&h=11b362ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171130/20230175</a>"},{"pid":"1c14db12380dd8b5337d8b7a6e757fe75aaa082b","tid":1672334,"uid":103618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd1a085e9819f9874fbe58948fb98a7f945b4c95","tid":1672334,"uid":103618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T04:56:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">唔想俾左膠外媒扭曲個集會<br />\n當場執生好過齋食事後丸<br />\n</span></span><br />\n在場人士唔該帶齊工具<br />\n- 各種警暴文宣標語（香港/加泰/各國）<br />\n- 各國國旗<br />\n- (Optional) 11月2日集會文宣<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">Do：</span></span><br />\n(1) 記得<ins>將注意力擺落警暴/人權問題 </ins><br />\n例如：標語唔好模糊用字齋寫「撐加泰」，要詳細講明撐咩（例如 #Police Brutality #Don'tLearnFromCCP ）<br />\n<br />\n(2) 如果有手足做左/講左啲咩好有詮釋空間既嘢，唔該幫手兜番<br />\n例如：舉加獨旗，唔該幫手舉埋各國國旗（人權係普世價值啊）<br />\n<br />\n(3) 如有搗亂份子，大家識執生<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Don't:</span></span><br />\n(1) 舉港獨旗<br />\n(2) 講加泰政治<br />\n<b